{"id":"vision","term":"Vision","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>(<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Luke 1:22\">Luke 1:22</a>), a vivid apparition, not a dream (comp. <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Luke 24:23\">Luke 24:23</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Acts 26:19\">Acts 26:19</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Corinthians 12:1\">2 Cor. 12:1</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Luke 1:22","Luke 24:23","Acts 26:19","2 Corinthians 12:1"]}